<template>
  <v-carousel :show-arrows="true">
    <v-carousel-item
      v-for="(item,i) in items"
      :key="i"
      :src="item.src"
    ></v-carousel-item>
  </v-carousel>
</template>

<script>

      return {
        items: [

          },
          {
            src: 'src="https://nerako.co/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/crazyhombre2-100x100.webp"',
          },
          {
            src: 'https://nerako.co/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/NINOS1.webp',
          },
          
        ],
      }
    },
  }
</script>
